# pyclaudir e2e credentials — gitignored, never commit real values.
#
# 1. Fill the E2E_BOT_* lines below (from @BotFather). Leave E2E_GROUP_ID=0.
# 2. Run:  .venv/bin/python tests/e2e/make_session.py
